nglo ([[Monitor Latino]])<ref>{{cite web|url=http://charts.monitorlatino.com/top20/Venezuela/Anglo/20200330\n}}</ref>\n| 3\n|}\n{{col-2}}\n\n=== Monthly charts ===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\"| Chart (2020)\n! scope=\"col\"| Peak<br />position\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Brazil ([[Pro-M\u00fasica Brasil]])<ref>{{cite web|url=https://pro-musicabr.org.br/home/top-50-streaming/?top50sPeriodo=03/2020/|title=Top 50 Streaming (Pro-M\u00fasica Brasil) \u2013 Mar\u00e7o de 2020|publisher=[[Associa\u00e7\u00e3o Brasileira de Produtores de Discos]]|accessdate=4 March 2020|language=Portuguese}}</ref>\n| 33\n|}\n{{col-end}}\n\n== Release history ==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\"\n! scope=\"col\"| Region\n! scope=\"col\"| Date\n! scope=\"col\"| Format\n! scope=\"col\"| Label\n! scope=\"col\" class=\"unsortable\" |{{abbr|Ref.|References}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Various\n| rowspan=\"2\"| February 28, 2020\n| {{hlist|[[Music download|Digital download]]|[[streaming media|streaming]]|[[Phonograph record|vinyl]]|[[Cassette tape|cassette]]|[[CD single]]}}\n| [[Interscope Records|Interscope]]\n| style=\"text-align:center\"| <ref name=\"Variety\" /><ref>{{cite web |title=Lady Gaga Official Shop |url=https://shop.ladygaga.com/ |accessdate=February 28, 2020 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200302132546/https://shop.ladygaga.com/ |archivedate=March 2, 2020 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Italy\n| rowspan=\"3\" | [[Contemporary hit radio]]\n| rowspan=\"3\" | [[Universal Music Group|Universal]]\n| style=\"text-align:center\"| <ref>{{cite web|url=http://radiodate.it/radio-date/lady-gaga-stupid-love-200259-28-02-2020-radiodate/|title=Lady Gaga - Stupid Love (Radio Date: February 28, 2020)|website=Radio Airplay Italia|access-date=February 28, 2020 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200229152729/http://radiodate.it/radio-date/lady-gaga-stupid-love-200259-28-02-2020-radiodate/ |archivedate=Februar